These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, milk, coffee
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, librarian, pilot, videographer
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, turquise, black, aquamarine
4 different games are played: chess, poker, billiard, canasta
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, hamster, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, handball, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, subway, tram
 1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 2. the person who likes turquise is the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person drinking milk is not the person driving the car##6
 4. the person driving the subway is not the person drinking water##6
 5. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 7. the person driving the tram is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
 8. the person playing chess is the coach##1
 9. the pilot is not the person drinking coffee##6
10. the videographer is the person driving the car##1
11. the pilot is the person driving the boat##1
12. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
14. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
15. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
16. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the tram##7
17. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person playing chess##6
18. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
19. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere between the coach and the person who's sport is baseball##7
20. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person drinking coffee##6
21. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage          | sprite      | coffee   | water     | milk |
| Job           | videographer | librarian   | coach    | pilot     |
| Color   | aquamarine       | black | emerald   | turquise   |
| Game   | billiard      | canasta     | chess | poker    |
| Pet           | chinchilla   | mouse       | hamster  | cat       |
| Sport         | baseball     | cycling     | handball | parkour   |
| Transport     | car          | subway      | tram     | boat      |

