 9. the person who likes ivory is not the person traveling to prague##6
10. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
11. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
12. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
13. the person traveling to marseilles is not the person watching zombie movies##6
14. the person eating kiwi is the firefighter##1
15. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the spanish##7
16. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
17. the colombian is the person watching romance movies##1
18. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who likes black##1
19. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
20. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the pilot##5
